### 10. **Configuration File Layout**

**Standard OpenClaw config structure:**
```yaml
channels:
  irc:
    # Base account (default)
    host: "irc.libera.chat"
    port: 6667
    tls: true
    nick: "openclaw-bot"
    username: "openclaw"

    # Accounts (named instances)
    accounts:
      work:
        host: "irc.example.com"
        nick: "bot-work"

    # DM/pairing policy
    dmPolicy: "pairing"
    allowFrom:
      - "!admin@*.example.com"

    # Group (channel) policy
    groupPolicy: "allowlist"
    groupAllowFrom:
      - "#general"
      - "#developers"

    # Per-channel config
    groups:
      "#general":
        tools: "enabled"
        allowFrom: ["*"]

    # Defaults
    defaultTo: "#general"
